{"tid":746081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 消夜男力戰攞你命3000","createTime":"2018-07-17T09:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T12:22:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"591cd801b00841c7aae001af90cd7eeba32dc4c1","tid":746081,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180717/20452093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F20452093&d=dY1SNdcIbrVQgb7bjg36Ef1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=a013f825\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F20452093&h=b4538592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180717/20452093</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月17日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n消夜男力戰攞你命3000<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180717/large/a1104b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180717%2Flarge%2Fa1104b.gif&h=982bba61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■兩男子一個手持利剪，另一人則握豉油樽圍住事主。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旺角噚日凌晨兩點幾發生血案！兩枱食客喺登打士街一間粉麵舖消夜，有人講嘢大聲嘈到隔籬枱，兩枱人嗌起上嚟，有人隨手擸起鉸剪拮落對方左邊臉近眼角，半邊臉披血。行兇嘅惡男之後同三個同伴帶埋把鉸剪走咗去，警方追緝緊佢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180717/large/a1104c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180717%2Flarge%2Fa1104c.gif&h=5481baff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■事主被襲至血流披面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n懷疑傷人之後走咗去嘅男人大約1.8米高，事發時着住淺色衫。讀者譚先生經過見到兩班人「講數」，當時39歲姓張男人左邊臉都係血，俾三個男人圍住，一個揸鉸剪，另一個手執玻璃樽，隨時攞你命3000。揸鉸剪男鬧傷者：「我冇攞威，我係被動，係嚟食嘢！」對方指「我都係嚟食嘢！」鉸剪男火起：「你食嘢，你冇得罪我哋？我哋嚟食嘢，你XX我哋！」，再鬧爆「我就唔X放佢&hellip;&hellip;我要個公道！」<br />\n<br />\n企喺傷者隔籬嘅男性朋友代佢求情，雙手合十向鉸剪男講咗句「大哥」，鉸剪男都唔肯罷休，差人到場前佢先走。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 法國躉佔領中區　警車戒備<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點●即聽"},{"pid":"8f9b51c6f557c19ce7a1874485bd42686f017abb","tid":746081,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"有相有證據但永遠捉不到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac6effedd54edbe02c9ce8bf698ac333b927a60","tid":746081,"uid":30169,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f9b51c6f557c19ce7a1874485bd42686f017abb","tid":746081,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"有相有證據但永遠捉不到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"可能又係休班狗"},{"pid":"7c6c5c238c2fcb6d99978151a4568e4343575d5f","tid":746081,"uid":98386,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"周街cctv點走得甩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c0213c5e26e509019fd49cce839ab6463be699","tid":746081,"uid":170223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:59:24.000Z","msg":"消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c43cc2c91ebf8c0b39525b3065e47dfb23e60cd","tid":746081,"uid":47147,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:04:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fd137117dc633c2d7cf42c91a38832b2ff17710","tid":746081,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c6c5c238c2fcb6d99978151a4568e4343575d5f","tid":746081,"uid":98386,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"周街cctv點走得甩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"你估龜仔真係會做正經野咩 傷者唔係有錢人同高官邊有人理"},{"pid":"7589dbcf137e321fea0b2cc8fe776ecc335927e0","tid":746081,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fd137117dc633c2d7cf42c91a3